{"tid":226971,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【日文歌改詞2】我啱啱用廣東話強姦咗Silent Majority首歌，跪求高手修改","createTime":"2017-05-02T22:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T06:18:21.000Z","uid":35370,"like":12,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa66cb8aecd50df612193325aa87f9685b74a441","tid":226971,"uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:18:30.000Z","msg":"Youtube 欅坂46 Silent Majority／沉默的多數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6ABMtg_nsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw6ABMtg_nsU&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=51c19174\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6ABMtg_nsU</a><br />\n<br />\n頭先溫溫下書比 部屋右牆角 巴打引誘我去改詞<br />\n用咗兩個鐘時間劣改首聖詩出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知好核突，可唔可以求下你哋集思修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b445d6927b257398c76272fce954e9abad06ed11","tid":226971,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:23:07.000Z","msg":"btw照舊有啲位係改咗音，因為日文好難完全轉廣東話<br />\n遲下會錄demo上嚟講下點唱<br />\n<br />\n都知有啲位好難頂，希望搵人幫下手改改佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c96f7a22f753c3a7752b13a8741c9e2c711a2ef","tid":226971,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"Demo如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講明先，我唱歌好難聽，唔打算負責唱<br />\n只係用嚟唱個樣本出嚟，比大家知啲詞係點唱<br />\n召喚靚聲巴打絲打幫手唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50997ba9221ef662ee3126f4e2ad082dac6e835","tid":226971,"ui